## Installing tools with help of 'installr'

The [installr] package provides function for installing external software on the _Microsoft Windows_ operating system.  This is a one-line interface to it and any package installation is automagically taken care of.

```r
# Install Pandoc
source('http://callr.org/installr#pandoc')

# Install latex2rtf
source('http://callr.org/installr#latexrtf')
```

[installr]: http://cran.r-project.org/package=installr
